findings.title: Sending tokens to dead address instead of real burn (decreasing total supply)
findings.description: Tokens are sent to a dead address rather than being burned, resulting in an incorrect total supply.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the marketing address.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing, burn and liquidity fee
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify marketing, burn, and liquidity fees, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change _liquifyThreshhold value
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the _liquifyThreshhold value.

findings.title: Owner can change marketingWalletToken address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the marketingWalletToken address.

findings.title: Owner can change _maxBalance value
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the _maxBalance value, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain entities or transactions from paying fees.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from max balance
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain addresses or wallets from the maximum balance, which could lead to unfair advantages or manipulation.
